task.summary: Default task
Edited GulpFile to conform to JSHint
Got workflow automation more or less completed. Started developing.
Set up components for Captivate Extra. Started work on Variable Manager. Set up a few library variables.
Changed workflow to automatically handle build numbers and version numbers
Got local and session storage variables working. Still have to fix bug with text entry boxes
Added files for more managers, created the Callback class to manage the callback functionality I was implementing frequently.
Added capacity to use Jasmine Unit Testing with Karma
Main.js now handles init for both Captivate and Storyline. Unit testing for main.js
Refactored to allow modules to identify themselves as belonging to a certain software. In unit tests it will allow them to register with the same name, but in production this will cause an error.
Local and session storage variables now work in Captivate and Storyline
Set up a lot of architecture for dealing with slide objects and creating proxies of them so that the same code can be used to deal with slide objects from Captivate and Storyline.
Started working on the behaviour manager, which manages changes in the natural behaviour of Captivate or Storyline and ensures these features are tied into a variable which can be turned on or off.
Implemented slide object finding for Captivate
Ended first stage of Slide Object locating in Captivate
Implemented hide, show, enable, disable and changeState command variables.
Implemented enterSlide callback for Captivate
Progressed on automatic state swapping
Fully implemented automatic state swapping and started implementing the slide object model.
Changed Naming
Implemented posX and posY Command variables.
Many bug fixes
CpExtra 1.2.0
CpExtra 1.2.0
Fixed SCORM Headless bug
Fixed Audio Ended event not firing while timeline is playing bug
Merged timeManager with movieStatusManager
Fixed enhanced object states not working on first slide when loaded headlessly
Last version to use pre Captivate 9.0.2 states
Fixed drag and drop bug, depreciated InterruptedClickEventHandler, made xprefPreventPlaybarScrubbing work when resizing project.
Almost fixed xcmndPosX and xcmndPosY for 9.0.2
Workflow automatically replaces cpextra javascript files in test files
Click and double click events now dispatch on slide objects in mobile courses
